div.p:
—a large number of expensive items (such as silver flatware) have been
                            ordered for the house, without consultation with Armao or the Shah, and the bills have
                            been presented to Armao;

—the hotel bill has included a charge of $10,000 for two small “shacks”
                            on the property where the Shah is staying (Gabriel Lewis property), even though these structures
                            have no apparent connection with the hotel;
